&lt;p&gt;MOUNT VERNON HOSPITAL&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;NEUROLOGY REHABILATION WARD&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;STAFF NURSES&lt;br /&gt;Full Time and Part Time Posts available&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for highly self-motivated, enthusiastic nurses with excellent communication skills to join us on this exciting opportunity. Successful candidates will participate in all ward/department activities as an effective team member whilst also supporting the senior nursing staff. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Post holders will be required to work within a well-established multidisciplinary team. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You must be flexible, reliable and have a professional caring manner. Opportunities for development are available in line with your yearly PDR reviews.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you are newly qualified or an experienced Band 5 nurse and are ready for new challenge, then look no further, we want to hear from you. This is a great opportunity to enhance your skills and knowledge further in neurosciences.&lt;/p&gt;
